            "author_association": "NONE",
            "body": "I am also able to reproduce this on `NVIM v0.11.0-dev-482+g7381f0a1d5`, on Arch linux, using the nvim-git package, following the steps mentioned by @haolian9.\r\n\r\nI found this bug while debugging a plugin for which `vim.api.nvim_buf_get_mark(current_buffer, \">\")` was apparently reporting the wrong column number (not line number as in this case), but perhaps they could be related.",
